author: Minecraft
description:
Ever felt the need to explore more of the world beneath the surface? Well, here’s your chance!
Join Gameplay Tech Lead Felix Jones, Gameplay Engineers Elias Wickander and Elisabeth Gangenes, and Game Artist Sarah Boeving as they present the nautilus – an aquatic wonder you can befriend and ride! Learn how it conserves your oxygen, why pufferfish are important, about its vibrant colors, and how tasty escargot inspired its design! See if you can find your first nautilus and unleash your submerged creativity (but beware of the zombie nautilus)!

Mounts of Mayhem  will be released on December 9.
title: ALL ABOUT THE NAUTILUS
